             was indicted for <rs id="t18300527-120-off643" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300527-120-off643" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300527-120-off643" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18300527-120-cd644" type="crimeDate">19th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300527-120-off643 t18300527-120-cd644"></join>, 1 sovereign, 1 half-crown, 4 sixpences, and 1 purse, value 2d., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300527-120-victim1034" type="victimName">
                           Samuel 
                           Bridge
                        <interp inst="t18300527-120-victim1034" type="surname" value="Bridge"></interp>
